data.description: Natural light flows throughout this wonderfully updated 2nd floor Ranch Townhome. Enjoy open concept living with a living/dining room combo, highlighted by vaulted ceilings and a cozy fireplace. Relax in a spacious primary suite with private access to the outdoor balcony. The updated kitchen features stainless steel appliances, granite countertops and ample storage space. Tucked away between private neighborhoods this low maintenance living offers both privacy and convenience. Quick access to Batavia HS, Randall Rd, I88 and major shopping. Move in ready & quick close possible!
